195
00:13:56,250 --> 00:13:59,860
First, learn to trade counter to the crowd.

196
00:13:59,860 --> 00:14:05,820
Look for opportunities where most retail traders
are positioned one way, and try to time your

197
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:11,230
