199
00:14:16,380 --> 00:14:18,860
How do you spot institutional activity?

200
00:14:18,860 --> 00:14:22,580
Use volume analysis for buying/selling signs.

201
00:14:22,580 --> 00:14:29,490
Pay close attention to volume spikes and other
volume clues to identify when smart money

202
00:14:29,490 --> 00:14:33,310
