203
00:14:33,310 --> 00:14:35,920
Trade with them, not against them.

204
00:14:35,920 --> 00:14:36,920
Third.

205
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:39,959
Set stops outside of obvious levels.

206
00:14:39,959 --> 00:14:46,800
Don't stack stops right on major support/resistance,
