207
00:14:46,800 --> 00:14:50,329
Leave some buffer room to avoid stop runs.

208
00:14:50,329 --> 00:14:52,509
Focus on big volume markets.

209
00:14:52,509 --> 00:14:55,390
These are harder for big players to manipulate.

210
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:58,709
And always be on the lookout for liquidity
grabs.

211
00:14:58,709 --> 00:15:04,759
Watch for sudden moves that trigger stops,
then reversals that benefit those who sold

212
00:15:04,759 --> 00:15:08,779
